n>无因生，<span class="_ _d"></span>进而抉择诸</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y12c ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">法是无生空性。<span class="_ _8"></span>具体来讲，<span class="_ _8"></span>倘若万法是自己产生自己，<span class="_ _8"></span>就会</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y12d ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls5f ws0">有无穷生的过失；若是依他而生，黑<span class="ls60">暗中也可以产生光</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yca ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">明……这种推理方法，<span class="_ _8"></span>在月称论师的<span class="_ _8"></span>《入中论》<span class="_ _8"></span>中讲得很细</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ycb ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">致。<span class="_ _d"></span>既然万法的<span class="_ _d"></span>“产生”无有实体，<span class="_ _8"></span>那么它的“存在”<span class="_ _8"></span>也不</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ydf ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">成立，<span class="_ _d"></span>最后的<span class="_ _d"></span>“灭亡”<span class="_ _d"></span>也没有，<span class="_ _d"></span>通过这种金刚屑因，<span class="_ _d"></span>就可以</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y12a ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">抉择一切为空性。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
